]

=== Topics This Week

- The Qabalah as a universal map of consciousness
- Introduction to the Tree of Life structure
- Microcosm and Macrocosm on the Tree

#inner-work[
  *Path Meditation*

  Meditate with one Major Arcana card each week this month. For Week 1, choose *The
  Magician (Key 1)*. Do not think *about* the card — sit with it, look at it, and
  allow its imagery to interact with your inner attention.

  Record what arises in your Tarot journal. This practice of meditating with
  symbolic images is one of the most ancient methods of inner development.
]

